metadata.name: Raggedy Army  #1
metadata.description:
The Raggedy Army consists of 7,777 Rag Dolls that were given life to bring balance to the Aethirverse. They live alongside many types of dangerous creatures and do not serve Good or Evil.

Aethirverse is a sci-fi/fantasy & post-apocalyptic NFT project with a story that is ever evolving and mysteries that are uncovered over time. Roadmap includes passive staking, a Play-to-Enjoy game, a cross-project marketplace, private node, a graphic novel/comic, and so much more.
Website: http://www.aethirverse.com/
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/aethirverse
Genesis Collection: https://www.opensea.io/collection/aethirwars
Artist, Nuetosis: https://www.twitter.com/nuetosis
